title: Mushijo
description:
The main character, Hinako Yomotsuki, is a high school girl who loves the anime "Puri Puri" and devotes all her energy into otaku activities. However, in actuality, when she unites with a mysterious "Maji" centipede life form, she becomes a distorted hero who saves people. Now she fights both to save the town assailed by "Maji" and to protect her unrequited crush, Himoru-senpai. 

[MangaDex page](https://mangadex.org/title/daa23083-4799-4bcf-8687-41c7f909ed19/mushijo)
author: Aniki
